name: should complete the eBooking flow from search to delivered status
fullName: should complete the eBooking flow from search to delivered status

steps.name: assert expected **<input.select-trigger.ng-untouched.ng-pristine.ng-valid>** to have value **SIN - Singapore Changi**
type CDG - Paris Charles de Gaulle, {delay: 150}
assert expected **[ <kt-search-button>, 1 more... ]** to have a length at least **2**
log Modal is present, attempting to close...
assert expected **.booking-details-popup** not to exist in the DOM
log Clicking Book button (ignoring disabled state if needed)...
assert expected **<button#btn-book.mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger.btn.btn-action.btn-pill.action-accept.mb-3.mat-mdc-tooltip-disabled>** to exist in the DOM
log  Waiting for status: BOOKING CONFIRMED
assert expected **Booking Confirmed** to match /BOOKING CONFIRMED/i
assert expected **BOOKING CONFIRMED** to equal **BOOKING CONFIRMED**
log  Waiting for status: IN TRANSIT
assert expected **IN TRANSIT** to match /IN TRANSIT/i
assert expected **IN TRANSIT** to equal **IN TRANSIT**
log  Waiting for status: AT DESTINATION
assert expected **AT DESTINATION** to match /AT DESTINATION/i
assert expected **AT DESTINATION** to equal **AT DESTINATION**
